The '''Draflago''' were a [[Sentience/Legends|sentient]] [[Species/Legends|species]] from the [[Draflago system/Legends|Draflago system]] that was active in [[The galaxy/Legends|the galaxy]] in the early years of the [[Galactic Empire/Legends|Galactic Empire]]. The [[Tion Hegemony/Legends|Tion Hegemony's]] sole university, the [[University of Rudrig/Legends|University of Rudrig]], had a number of luxury mud tanks available for visiting Draflago.<ref name="HLL">''[[Han Solo and the Lost Legacy]]'', 24.</ref>

==Behind the scenes==
The Draflago were first mentioned in ''[[Han Solo and the Lost Legacy]]'', a [[Brian Daley]] novel published by [[Del Rey]] in [[1980]].

